google_1326.nl_query:
How many members of the Student_Club have majored Environmental Engineering?
 'Environmental Engineering' is the major name
google_1326.golden_query: SELECT COUNT(T1.member_id) FROM member AS T1 INNER JOIN major AS T2 ON T1.link_to_major = T2.major_id WHERE T2.major_name = 'Environmental Engineering'
